{"title":"一棵柳树变成林","authors":["章明"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":9,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵柳树变成林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"章明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳条儿长，柳叶儿青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边一座柳树林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳荫深处有哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海防春来花似锦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们指点柳树林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷说起种树的人："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老班长千里去探家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带回柳枝到边境。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳枝种在大海边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发芽抽条枝叶深，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"折下柳条插下土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年五载成了林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵柳树变成林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋挡风雨夏遮阴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老班长离开边疆地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下了一颗忠诚的心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学柳树到处生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎下深根在边境！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学忠诚的老班长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心为革命！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}